name: BabyLog
0:
”Alexa ask Baby Log to log wet diaper.”
”Alexa ask Baby Log when did I last nurse.”
”Alexa start baby log.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby log
des: Keep a journal for your babies activities - nursing, feeding, diaper change, sleep and more. Easily find out which breast side to nurse from. Get stats on solid or wet diapers to see if you need to call the pediatrician or if things are in order.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
